{"tid":1515061,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰更新員工守則　鼓勵舉報違反守則情況","createTime":"2019-08-29T03:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T08:37:54.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"64386cd5095e9c84bb8c52c1246864d1eb5111e6","tid":1515061,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:50:31.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】國泰航空更新員工行為守則，表明對員工參與非法活動會採取零容忍的態度，又鼓勵員工舉報任何懷疑違反守則的情況。<br />\n<br />\n國泰向員工發內部通告，指近日有關解僱員工的報道中有很多錯誤資訊，令員工感到焦慮，公司不會評論個別個案，但向員工保證，解僱決定是經過高層正式及謹慎檢視。國泰對員工參與非法活動會採取零容忍的態度，亦不容許員工使用公司資源表達政治意見。<br />\n<br />\n通告指出，公司需要建立服從的文化，因此鼓勵員工舉報身邊任何懷疑違反守則的情況，公司會跟進調查並保護舉報人的身分。"},{"pid":"d6f5db3ecf6471cc1d1d39b089d9c129f0315d91","tid":1515061,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:50:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NEBkNLNxwx8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNEBkNLNxwx8&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=77d9a7b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NEBkNLNxwx8</a>"},{"pid":"975b9ac79af37b30178ce389fb51e50ab61d5b9d","tid":1515061,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:50:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=360861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360861&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=9eaaae34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360861&h=81061ec5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=360861</a>"},{"pid":"2684d1cb2d11874a832ffa75dde53e0512452a6d","tid":1515061,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:52:19.000Z","msg":"民革式批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6729cf53fc681fc8a97dfb40aaf401bf395b72b3","tid":1515061,"uid":193471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:37:54.000Z","msg":"其實國泰都係被迫<br />\n說好的不割呢"}]}